=======
Changes
=======


0.3.0 (*2022-08-07*)
====================

- cli: fix #1, exit codes are now propagated from click.


0.2.0 (*2022-04-21*)
====================

- reporter: RichReporter, with color output and progress bar support.
- linter: integration with pyflakes, pycodestyle and flake8.
- cli: CliGroup, changes in basic usage API.


0.1.0 (*2022-04-15*)
====================

Not released, part of SciPy `do.py`

- cli: click integration with class based defintion.